@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFF3E0
skinparam classBorderColor #E65100
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Delivered
Delivered --> Draft : process
Delivered : entry / log warehouse
Draft --> Approved : update
Approved --> Archived : process
Archived --> Pending : confirm
Pending --> [*]
@enduml